.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, green, red, white, yellow
There are 5 different nationalities: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: western, satire, musical, spy, family
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: rose, amaryllis, zinnia, orchid, dahlia
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, october, august, march, february
1. the british is the person who likes red
2. the swedish is the person who's birthday is in august
3. the danish is the person watching spy movies
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes white
5. the person who likes green is the person watching satire movies
6. the person who growszinnia is the person who's birthday is in october
7. the person who likes yellow is the person who growsamaryllis
8. the person watching musical movies is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january
11. the person who's birthday is in februarys is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis
12. the person who growsrose is the person watching western movies
13. the german is the person who growsorchid
14. the norwegian is on the left or right of the person who likes blue
15. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person watching family movies

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| Birthday		|     january	|    february	|     october	|     march	|      august	|
| Movie-Genre	|    family	|     spy	|     musical	|    satire	|      western	|
| Flower		|   amaryllis	|    dahlia	|  zinnia	|    orchid	|   rose	|
